comentario2 = "In the days I spend in Port Tanzia.. I remember there was a \"Green Nargacuga Lunatic\", everything he said was about it, everything he wore was about it.. I wonder where they're now.."
comentario2_br = "Nos dias que passei em Port Tanzia... lembro de um maluco obcecado pelo Green Nargacuga, tudo o que ele dizia, o que vestia.. Fico imaginando onde eles estão agora..."
